Reviews: Ok so its not value for money if you just use the concentrate; find a container, add concentrate, dilute with water, pour over everything in the house, wash container and find somewhere to store it so you remember what you used it for...none of that, if you use this. Pour it into cap, tip into plant. Lazy and the plants seem to love it.
